perl-Log-Message: perl-Log-Message (Powerful and flexible message storage mechanism)
perl-Log-Message:
perl-Log-Message: Log::Message is a generic message storage mechanism. It allows you to
perl-Log-Message: store messages on a stack and assign meta-data to it. Some meta-data
perl-Log-Message: will automatically be added for you, like a timestamp and a stack
perl-Log-Message: trace.
perl-Log-Message:
perl-Log-Message: For more info, visit: https://metacpan.org/release/Log-Message
